name: Love Is Loyal Black Crew Neck
description:
100% of Net Profit Donated

$15.00 toward our special cause!

"This shirt will help a dog walk again." A few months ago our friend Bobby's dog Minimus tore both of it's ACLs and it's meniscus rendering her unable to walk. Bobby rescued this dog from terrible abuse and neglect three years prior. Mini suffered these crippling injuries due to weakened tendons and ligaments as a result of malnutrition when she was a puppy. All profits raised by purchasing this item will go to our friend Bobby to help pay for the expensive operations to restore Minimus' ability to walk. •LIMITED EDITION •Poly-Cotton Blend (50% Polyester / 50% Cotton) construction
